A wrapper for the XMRig HTTP API

## Changelog
### 1.0.1
* Added the following properties
  * hashrate
  * uptime
  * accepted_jobs
  * rejected_jobs
  * paused
  * total_hashes
  * current_difficulty
  * pool_info
  * cpu_info
  * version
  * uptime_readable
  * memory_usage
  * load_average
### 1.0.2
* Added Access Token Support
